<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="imy1cz" data-vimeo-id="415358140" data-video-descrip="The Honest Trailer for &amp;quot;Batman v Superman&amp;quot; captures the true angst of this Superman." data-video-title="Angsty Superman" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/imy1cz_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/honest_trailer_angsty_superman_moment.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/AdaptationalAngstUpgrade" data-video-tropename="Adaptational Angst Upgrade" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="4.21" data-video-rating-count="14" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/HonestTrailers,Film/BatmanVSupermanDawnOfJustice,Franchise/Superman" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/honest_trailer_angsty_superman_moment.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Angsty Superman</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="38buvy" data-vimeo-id="415353085" data-video-descrip="The Honest Trailer for &amp;quot;Man of Steel&amp;quot; can't help but note that this movie is a notable tone shift from the last Superman movies." data-video-title="Honest Trailer- Man of Steel" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/38buvy_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/honest_trailers_man_of_steel_screenshot_5.png" data-video-trope="Main/DarkerAndEdgier" data-video-tropename="Darker and Edgier" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="4.67" data-video-rating-count="15" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/HonestTrailers,Film/ManOfSteel,Franchise/Superman" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/honest_trailers_man_of_steel_screenshot_5.png">
